header
  .bg
    .content
      .kolom
        .atas
            - var img = '../../static/img/icon/11.png'
            img(src=img)
   
        .tengah
          h2 We know what you want
        .bawah
          p
            | We have an excellent book search engine where everyone can find what they want at the moment. 
      .kolom
        .atas
            - var im1 = '../../static/img/icon/2.png'
            img(src=im1)
        .tengah
          h2 We have a rating of books
        .bawah
          p
            | The 21st century is a dynamic time, where you have to constantly evolve and here you have to run to stand still. Anyone who does not read good books has no advantage over someone who does not know how to read them.
      .kolom
        .atas
